Ceibo Apps
Ceibo Apps respects your privacy.

Data Collection by the App
This application does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal or sensitive user data.
The app does not require user accounts, does not include advertising, does not use analytics or tracking technologies, and does not communicate with external servers operated by the developer.

All functionality operates locally on the user’s device.
If the app requests device permissions (such as microphone, storage, or audio access), these permissions are used solely to provide the app’s core functionality. No data accessed through these permissions is collected, stored, or transmitted by Ceibo Apps.
Ceibo Apps does not share data with third parties.

Google Play & Google Payments
This app is distributed through Google Play.
Purchases and downloads are processed by Google and are subject to Google’s own privacy policies and terms.
Google may collect and process certain information independently, such as:
Purchase and transaction details
Device information
Country or region
Data required for payment processing, fraud prevention, refunds, or legal compliance

Ceibo Apps does not have access to, control over, or responsibility for data collected directly by Google as part of Google Play or Google Payments services.
For more information about how Google handles data, please review:
Google Privacy Policy
Google Play & Google Payments Privacy Notices

Changes to This Privacy Policy
If this Privacy Policy is updated, the revised version will be made available at this URL.

